    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Let's Play and Party with Lappy!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lappy, the beloved character from TBS TV’s <i>Love it!</i>, is now starring in a brand-new game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>LAPPY GAMES</i> is a fun-filled party action game where you compete to collect the most hearts with Lappy and friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 players at once, with full support for online multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the various stage events to your advantage—whoever collects the most hearts wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade collected hearts for items in the gacha, and build up your collection in the in-game encyclopedia—perfect for completionists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and easy-to-learn rules, it's a game everyone can enjoy. Gather your friends and family and get the party started!</p>",
